{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":811,"text":"Hi, I'm Jack,"},{"time":2509,"text":"and I'm transgender."},{"time":5232,"text":"Let me take a guess at some of thoughts"},{"time":7114,"text":"that might be running\nthrough your head right now."},{"time":9472,"text":"\"Transgender?"},{"time":10646,"text":"Wait, does that mean that they're\nactually a man or actually a woman?\""},{"time":13988,"text":"\"I wonder if he's had the surgery yet ..."},{"time":16656,"text":"Oh, now I'm looking at his crotch."},{"time":18323,"text":"Look to the right,\nthat's a safe place to look.\""},{"time":20682,"text":"\"Yes, I knew it!\nNo real man has hips like those.\""},{"time":23077,"text":"\"My friend's daughter is transgender --"},{"time":24997,"text":"I wonder if they know each other.\""},{"time":27155,"text":"\"Oh my gosh, he is so brave."},{"time":29990,"text":"I would totally support his right\nto use the men's bathroom."},{"time":32895,"text":"Wait, but how does he use the bathroom?"},{"time":34832,"text":"How does he have sex?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":36014,"text":"OK, OK, let's stop\nthose hypothetical questions"},{"time":39034,"text":"before we get too close for my comfort."},{"time":40958,"text":"I mean, don't get me wrong,"},{"time":42283,"text":"I did come here today to share\nmy personal experiences being transgender,"},{"time":45880,"text":"but I did not wake up this morning\nwanting to tell an entire audience"},{"time":49706,"text":"about my sex life."},{"time":51398,"text":"Of course, that's the problem\nwith being trans, right?"},{"time":54051,"text":"People are pretty much always\nwondering how we have sex"},{"time":56821,"text":"and what kind of equipment\nwe're working with below the belt."},{"time":60318,"text":"Being trans is awkward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63180,"text":"And not just because the gender\nI was assigned at birth"},{"time":65776,"text":"mismatches the one I really am."},{"time":67498,"text":"Being trans is awkward"},{"time":68825,"text":"because everyone else gets awkward\nwhen they're around me."},{"time":72512,"text":"People who support me and all other\ntrans people wholeheartedly"},{"time":76240,"text":"are often so scared to say to wrong thing,"},{"time":78527,"text":"so embarrassed to not know\nwhat they think they should,"},{"time":81131,"text":"that they never ask."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83263,"text":"Part of what was so nerve-racking\nabout coming out as transgender"},{"time":86568,"text":"was knowing that people\nwouldn't know what I meant."},{"time":90198,"text":"And when someone comes out as gay,"},{"time":91842,"text":"people know what that means,"},{"time":93227,"text":"but when you come out as trans,"},{"time":94796,"text":"you have to face the misconceptions"},{"time":96488,"text":"that will color other people's\nimpressions of you"},{"time":99012,"text":"even after you've educated them ..."},{"time":101376,"text":"And you will have to educate them."},{"time":103693,"text":"When I came out,"},{"time":104867,"text":"I wrote at 10-page encyclopedic document"},{"time":106876,"text":"with a zip-file attachment\nof music and videos"},{"time":109392,"text":"that I sent to every\nsingle person I came out to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111731,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112841,"text":"And I kept it in my email signature\nfor months afterwards,"},{"time":115625,"text":"because you also\ndon't ever stop coming out."},{"time":118109,"text":"I came out to the accountant\nhelping me with my taxes"},{"time":122070,"text":"and the TSA agents who didn't know\nwhich one of them should pat me down,"},{"time":125785,"text":"the man or the woman."},{"time":127902,"text":"I mean, I just came out\nto everyone watching this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131665,"text":"When I came out to my dad,"},{"time":133680,"text":"to my great relief, he was totally cool\nwith me being trans,"},{"time":136538,"text":"but as soon as I started talking\nabout physically transitioning,"},{"time":139808,"text":"he freaked."},{"time":140998,"text":"And I quickly realized it was because he,\nlike so many other people,"},{"time":144299,"text":"think that physical transition\nmeans just one thing:"},{"time":147749,"text":"the surgery."},{"time":149466,"text":"Now, listen,"},{"time":150640,"text":"if there were one magical surgery"},{"time":152467,"text":"that could turn me into a tall, muscular,"},{"time":155340,"text":"societally perfect image\nof a man overnight,"},{"time":158135,"text":"I'd sign up in a heartbeat."},{"time":160228,"text":"Unfortunately, it isn't that simple."},{"time":162502,"text":"There are dozens of different\ngender-affirming surgeries"},{"time":165505,"text":"from chest surgeries to bottom surgeries"},{"time":168304,"text":"to facial feminization and man-sculpting."},{"time":171263,"text":"Many trans people will only ever undergo\none procedure in their lifetime, if that."},{"time":175804,"text":"Maybe because they don't\npersonally feel the need"},{"time":178164,"text":"but also because they're expensive,"},{"time":180507,"text":"and health insurance\nis only beginning to cover them."},{"time":183620,"text":"Instead, the first step for a trans person\nseeking physical transition"},{"time":187414,"text":"is usually hormone replacement therapy."},{"time":190022,"text":"Hormones are why I have a deeper voice\nand some sparse whiskers on my neck"},{"time":194309,"text":"and a giant pimple on my chin."},{"time":197461,"text":"Basically, they put you\nthrough a second puberty ..."},{"time":200208,"text":"it's a blast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201469,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202602,"text":"Now, because our transitions\nare slower and steadier"},{"time":206263,"text":"than historic misconceptions\ncan lead people to believe,"},{"time":208923,"text":"there can be some confusion"},{"time":210242,"text":"about when to call someone\nby their new name and pronouns."},{"time":213302,"text":"There's no distinct point\nin physical transition"},{"time":216131,"text":"at which a trans person\nbecomes their true gender."},{"time":219234,"text":"As soon as they tell you\ntheir new name and pronouns,"},{"time":221743,"text":"that's when you start using them."},{"time":223735,"text":"It can be difficult to make the change."},{"time":225799,"text":"You might slip up here and there;"},{"time":227504,"text":"I've slipped up myself\nwith other trans people."},{"time":229878,"text":"But I always think to myself,"},{"time":231304,"text":"if we can change from calling\nPuff Daddy to P. Diddy,"},{"time":234822,"text":"and if we apologize profusely\nwhen we've used the wrong gender pronoun"},{"time":238910,"text":"for someone's pet cat --"},{"time":241005,"text":"I mean, I think we can make\nthe same effort"},{"time":243039,"text":"for the real humans in our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245143,"text":"Now, there is no topic that makes other\npeople more awkward about trans people"},{"time":250589,"text":"than public bathrooms."},{"time":253006,"text":"Ah, the bathrooms --"},{"time":254333,"text":"the latest political flash point\nfor LGBT opponents."},{"time":257308,"text":"Here's a fun fact about bathrooms:"},{"time":259471,"text":"more US congressmen have been convicted\nof assaulting someone in a public bathroom"},{"time":263794,"text":"than trans people have been."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265368,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":267495,"text":"The truth is we trans people are so much\nmore scared of you than you are of us."},{"time":271632,"text":"It's a huge point of discussion\nin trans communities"},{"time":274086,"text":"about which bathroom\nto start using and when,"},{"time":276258,"text":"so we don't attract attention\nthat could lead to violence against us."},{"time":279618,"text":"I personally started using the men's room"},{"time":281618,"text":"when I started getting confused\nand frightened looks in the women's room,"},{"time":286031,"text":"even though I was petrified\nto start going into the men's room."},{"time":289039,"text":"And often we opt to just\nnot go to the bathroom at all."},{"time":291799,"text":"A 2015 national survey of trans people"},{"time":294267,"text":"found that eight percent of us\nhad had a urinary tract infection"},{"time":297422,"text":"in the past year"},{"time":298677,"text":"as a result of avoiding restrooms."},{"time":301480,"text":"These bathroom bills\naren't protecting anyone."},{"time":304724,"text":"All they're doing"},{"time":305906,"text":"is ensuring that when trans people\nare assaulted in bathrooms,"},{"time":309250,"text":"the law will no longer be on our side\nwhen we report it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313169,"text":"Being trans means a daily onslaught\nof these misconceptions."},{"time":319334,"text":"And I have it pretty easy."},{"time":321071,"text":"I am a white, able-bodied guy"},{"time":323239,"text":"sitting nearly at the peak\nof privilege mountain."},{"time":327382,"text":"For non-binary people,"},{"time":329433,"text":"for trans women,"},{"time":331081,"text":"for trans people of color,"},{"time":333137,"text":"it is so much harder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336903,"text":"So I've given you a starter pack\nof trans knowledge"},{"time":339730,"text":"that I hope will lead\nto more learning on your own."},{"time":343608,"text":"Talk to trans people."},{"time":345653,"text":"Listen to us."},{"time":347587,"text":"Amplify our voices."},{"time":349934,"text":"Take the heat off of us\nand educate those around you"},{"time":352403,"text":"so we don't have to every time."},{"time":354957,"text":"Maybe someday, when I say,"},{"time":357144,"text":"\"Hi, I'm Jack, and I'm transgender,\""},{"time":360625,"text":"the only response I'll get is,"},{"time":362617,"text":"\"Hi, nice to meet you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":366256,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367431,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}